    <footer class="px-10 py-6 bg-gray-800 text-white">
      <div class="lg:flex">
        <div class="px-8">
          <img src="./img/logo.png" alt="Logo" />
          <p class="text-xs">
            Bankereum is a 100% decentralized global bank based on Ethereum
            blockchain technology, which already successfully unify professional
            traders, companies and individuals wishing to use cryptocurrencies
            without the risk of volatility on single platform. The software is
            based on Ethereum cryptocurrency and the transaction framework uses
            the latest Blockchain capabilities. Get all benefits of “digital
            gold” and more features with the world’s best crypto bank named
            ‘Bankereum’.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:pt-0 pt-10 lg:px-10">
          <h1 class="font-semibold text-2xl">Newsletter</h1>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-xs">
            Keep up to date with our progress. Subscribe for e-mail updates.
          </h4>
          <div class="">
            <input
              type="text"
